 that the \"Remember Me\" option doesn\'t align with the checkbox in Chinese. (I didn\'t test other languages.)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">The second thing is that the live preview doesn\'t show some of the words, like \"Register\". But in the actual login page it works.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">The third thing is that there isn\'t \"auto\" as the form height, which makes it weird in registeration as well as reset password form.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">The last thing is the form alignment options is switched: The left-right option actually represents top-bottom alignment and vice versa.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">But these are just small issues and except these the plugin works smoothly. Well done 👏</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Perfect</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 dari 5 bintang\" data-title-template=\"%s dari 5 bintang\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Oleh <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jpruehmann/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/471e473b6a5504b8607f5a9297bbe194?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/471e473b6a5504b8607f5a9297bbe194?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\