wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Really great functionality. Perfect to add a list of invitees and then get them all to the URL to confirm their attendance for a party. So much easier, than back and forth with a ton of repetitive messages.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thanks!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Perfect</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 dari 5 bintang\" data-title-template=\"%s dari 5 bintang\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Oleh <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dbonina/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6893f1bfc967312331a5db1e45b5b4c8?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6893f1bfc967312331a5db1e45b5b4c8?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dbonina/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">dbonina</a> pada <span class=\"review-date\">April 19, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All that I need for my daughter 15th birthday. Thanks.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Excellent, Straightforward plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 dari 5 bintang\" data-title-template=\"%s dari 5 bintang\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Oleh <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/djaychela/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/62f08e04231900892512c37ef40da420?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/62f08e04231900892512c37ef40da420?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/djaychela/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">djaychela</a> pada <span class=\"review-date\">Maret 25, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For the most part, this plugin worked really well - easy to set up if following the instructions, and allowed the quick creation of RSVPs for our wedding.  There are a couple of places where it could benefit from being more configurable (in terms of the boilerplate text being configurable, and the default styling needing some tweaking), but it\'s very good overall.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Grewat easy PlugIn for Events lists</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 dari 5 bintang\" data-title-template=\"%s dari 5 bintang\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Oleh <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/hfvienna/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/17b401b50ff5eb41a7933582801ef0bd?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/17b401b50ff5eb41a7933582801ef0bd?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/hfvienna/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">hfvienna</a> pada <span class=\"review-date\">Februari 16, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Just what I was looking for, simple , easy but customisable in free version even.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great plug-in</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 dari 5 bintang\" data-title-template=\"%s dari 5 bintang\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Oleh <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jsteltenpohl/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2e199a76665331f247693cdf1a4eb76f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2e199a76665331f247693cdf1a4eb76f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jsteltenpohl/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">jsteltenpohl</a> pada <span class=\"review-date\">Juni 29, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I utilized this plug-in on a relatives wedding website.  She was on a tight budget and I found that this plug-in provided everything that I needed.  I highly recommend.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Exceptional</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 dari 5 bintang\" data-title-template=\"%s dari 5 bintang\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Oleh <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/spiffysax/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5eb8de621ccf5c9a84729627bb686f5f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5eb8de621ccf5c9a84729627bb686f5f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/spiffysax/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">TraderHowell <small>(SpiffySax)</small></a> pada <span class=\"review-date\">Mei 26, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I can only speak for the free version of this plugin, but it works exceptionally well. It took a lot of code edits to get things dialed in just right, but the groundwork is laid out to make creating an RSVP page extremely easy. Thanks, dev!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">still amazing 3+ years later!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 dari 5 bintang\" data-title-template=\"%s dari 5 bintang\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Oleh <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mb2963/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/99e5e5c99b3856add4ec1ff988b20bc2?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/99e5e5c99b3856add4ec1ff988b20bc2?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mb2963/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">mb2963</a> pada <span class=\"review-date\">Maret 21, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I used this plugin for our daughter\'s wedding website in 2018-2019. Now, I\'m creating a website for our son\'s website... and the plugin is even better than it was before. Love how easy it makes it for me to upload the guest list. Guests love the ease of RSVP\'ing online. Can\'t believe the features I can use as a free plugin. Very grateful!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"revi